PrecisOrder directing the Minister of Public Works not to order that a public hearing be conducted with respect to the expropriation of some 5.05 hectares of marshland situated at CAPE JOURIMAIN, in the County of Westmorland, New Brunswick, in connection with the construction of a bridge linking the Provinces of New Brunswick and Prince Edward Island, as it would occasion a delay prejudicial to the public interest.
